import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import './index.css'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import App from './App'

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'))
root.render(
    <React.StrictMode>
        <BrowserRouter>
            <Routes>
                <Route path="/*" element={<App />} />
            </Routes>
        </BrowserRouter>
    </React.StrictMode>
)
